# Project: tokiSync — Caveman Rules

# 📌 SECTION 0: CONTEXT
Start session: Read AI_AGENT_CONTEXT.md (SSOT), PROJECT_HANDOVER_MASTER.md.
AI_AGENT_CONTEXT.md = Single Source of Truth.

# 📌 SECTION 0.1: ENV
Terminal command: Use `export PATH=$PATH:/usr/local/bin`. Mac path safety.

# 🚨 SECTION 1: PERMISSIONS
- 🚫 PROHIBITED: `clasp push`, `rm -rf`, `git push`. DO NOT AUTO-RUN. Guide human.
- ✅ ALLOWED: `ls`, `cat`, `grep`, `find`, `git status`. Read-only OK.
- ⚠️ CONDITIONAL: `npm test`, `build`. Run after plan approval.

# 📝 SECTION 2: DOCS
- Real-time: Unit done → Update `.agent_checkpoint.md`. External memory.
- Final: Sync `.agent_checkpoint.md` to CONTEXT/HANDOVER/CHANGELOG. Delete temp.
- HANDOVER > 300 lines → Move old to CHANGELOG. Keep lean.

# 📂 SECTION 2.1: STRUCTURE
- All MD (except root SSOT) → `documentation/`.
- `guides/`: How-to. `reports/`: walkthrough. `archive/`: history.
- Root SSOT: README, CHANGELOG, CONTEXT, HANDOVER. Update README map.

# 🔒 SECTION 3: EDITORIAL
No shadow echoing. Use actual tools. Human = Final pipeline runner.

# 🔍 SECTION 4: AUDIT
Post-coding: Logic verify. Edge case check. Report in walkthrough/report.

# 🛠️ SECTION 5: SKILLS
- Planning: @[concise-planning], @[wiki-architect].
- Code: @[javascript-pro], @[tailwind-patterns].
- Perf/Debug: @[performance-engineer], @[systematic-debugging].
- Security: @[security-auditor], @[vibe-code-auditor].

# 🤖 SECTION 6: AGENTS
1. Main (Claude/Pro): Strategy. Planning.
2. Worker (Flash): Implementation. Atomic tasks.
3. Auditor (3 Pro): Inspect. Edge cases. PASS/FAIL report.

# 🔄 SECTION 7: ERRORS
Error found → Auditor report → Main re-plan → Worker re-impl. No quick fixes.

# 📝 SECTION 8: HANDOVER
Model swap: Update `.agent_checkpoint.md`. Read SSOT + state first.

# 🚀 SECTION 9: RELEASE & BRANCH
- Main: No direct commit. Use PR.
- Assets: Include dist/tokiSync.user.js, dist/TokiSync_Server_Bundle.gs in Release.
- 🚫 NO AUTO-COMMIT/RELEASE. Bump version @ COMMIT phase ONLY after human approval.
